Feature: Genetic Mash-Up Pets
    As a mad scientist customer,
    I want to know what pets I can combine
    So that I can order them for my lair.

    Acceptance Criteria:
    1. mad scientist chooses a normal pet from a list, and
       receives mash-up pet list with name and abilities.
    2. Mammals can only be mashed up with mammals, fish with fish, and reptiles with reptiles.

    Exercise: translate above criteria into Gherkin scenarios, then implement them using the ATDD cycle